 />\n本身是醫生的公民黨立法會議員郭家麒指，香港確實存在濫用抗生素情況，「事實上係一個全球都有嘅問題，只不過（與中國大。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dxHIP-WNINRHrAYxxgKf2higVBo=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JV4LT5ONXVAQZPT23Z5ECULSFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdxHIP-WNINRHrAYxxgKf2higVBo%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJV4LT5ONXVAQZPT23Z5ECULSFI.jpg&h=e34c3134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■齡記《新思維通識》「公共衞生」單元有關沙士的內容曾作修訂。"},{"pid":"a390bf8ff987bd57485a76b4387f2e9ed300f59b","tid":2165849,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"通識變通通都唔識<br />\n不過香港教育是Q但啦<br />\n有能力既一早送走左班仔女"}]}